{
  "stem": "25423.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was already given this false name, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was kept locked up in this cell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My only contact was, was a priest, monk priest, who was teaching me language.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't speak Ukrainian, custom, culture, how to pray, and things of that sort.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was, in a way, quickly trained to be adapted to my surrounding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I used to go to the refectory to have meals with the monks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could wander around the monastery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, maybe not, because they thought that maybe I'm a novice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, slowly and gradually, it became clear to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time I had my own clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the food-- I ate the food of the monastery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This, you see--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] --The question was not, you see, to have kosher food, but to have food to survive the day, first of all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And secondly, the monks did not worry about providing me with kosher food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You couldn't, because, you see, I was observed all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The minute I would start-- [LAUGHS] --You see, any religious practices, I would endanger the whole community and myself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Myself.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My false name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew that this is my name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the same way, my brother knew that he had his name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was different from mine in order not to make any connection in case either of us is caught.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Were you in the same monastery?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in constant fear, constant fear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So were they.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They were afraid that if I am caught, they will be shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] How does one learn to be a Ukrainian?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very simple.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, as long as you realize that your life depends on it, you learn very quickly.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
